§I tunables
  AccessibilityTunables ⊗
    heat_shimmer    : f32 ∈ [0,1] default 0.50
    smoke_density   : f32 ∈ [0,1] default 0.50
    hammer_volume   : f32 ∈ [0,1] default 1.00
    bloom_intensity : f32 ∈ [0,1] default 0.35
    fog_intensity   : f32 ∈ [0,1] default 0.10
    subtitle_duration : f32 ∈ [0,1] (normalized · 16s-scale · default 4s)
    safe_mode       : bool default false ; toggle hard-zeros visual-axes
    closed_captions_enabled : bool default true (axiom)

§I keymap-canonical (32 entries · stable-order)
  Movement   : W A S D Space LCtrl LShift
  Modal      : Esc Tab ` / Backspace Enter
  Render     : F1-F10 (modes 0-9) · F12 (screenshot) · P (polarization-5-cycle)
  Capture    : F7-tour · F8-video · F9-burst · F12-screenshot
  Atmospheric: C (CFER-toggle) · F11 (fullscreen)
  Menu-nav   : ArrowUp ArrowDown ArrowLeft ArrowRight Enter

